name: Love!t (15ml)
description:
Natural non-irritating transdermal oil — it has the unique ability to penetrate deep into the skin tissue all the way to the cellular level without irritating sensitive tissue.

Powerful anti-inflammatory — as Emu Oil penetrates, it helps to relieve inflammation not only on the surface of the skin but also deep into the muscles and joints as well.

Wonderful moisturizer — our pure Emu Oil replenishes the skin's natural oils and adds vital moisture to dry, damaged tissue.

Natural source of Omega 3, 6, and 9 — these important fatty acids moisturize, nourish, soothe, and protect the skin.

Transdermal carrier — Emu Oil has the ability to carry itself and other added ingredients along with it into the body.

High purity level — our pure Emu Oil is Non-Toxic, Hypo-Allergenic, Non-Comedogenic (won't clog your pores), a Non-Ocular Irritant (won't irritate your eyes) and is Bio-Degradable (eco friendly).
